{"tid":2037914,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"大家用咩電郵去申請VPN","createTime":"2020-05-27T08:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T16:11:41.000Z","uid":73671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"75f5a2545229836cfca5973391363137f3816b92","tid":2037914,"uid":73671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T08:55:00.000Z","msg":"大家係咪都會申請個新Email去用VPN？<br />\n<br />\n我見好多人講 開個新嘅Email安全啲<br />\n大部分推薦用 protonmail / tutanota<br />\n係咪即使申請佢地免費帳號都好過 用gmail/ yahoo 呢啲"},{"pid":"c2b9537547d2763258662ed4fc02f9a0dcd1f1d5","tid":2037914,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"23cf7135113c21eca69f6e537dc6de90a04e839b","tid":2037914,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Surfshark 回應 VPN 間歇出現斷線的問題</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5kKD1r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5kKD1r.png&h=4bc351c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7cb9P8F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7cb9P8F.png&h=01404cc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcQKD11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcQKD11.png&h=91553329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dFwxNVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdFwxNVn.png&h=f0539429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pJAuP83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpJAuP83.png&h=46924d3c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：但閂咗會有機會洩露真 IP<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yp34D2z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyp34D2z.png&h=87ec92fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：但安全同樣好重要<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nn1Ri2P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnn1Ri2P.png&h=4c3d9a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：閂咗 kill switch 就做唔到匿名上網<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rPSEsW4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrPSEsW4.png&h=cc988ead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：咁可唔可以將上述提到嘅問題轉述俾有關部門<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JrxNXk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JrxNXk.png&h=4ccfcbb2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n結論：單從服務態度而言，<br />\n未 join Surfshark 嘅人唔洗考慮了，<br />\n至於 join 咗嘅如果有我上圖提到嘅問題，<br />\n就盡快喺由購買日起計 30 日內上 live chat 搞退款。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">咁用邊間好？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. TunnelBear<br />\n有做年度安全審核，<br />\n但無雙重 VPN，<br />\n亦無 iKEv2 同 Wireguard，<br />\n近年更被 mcafee 收購，<br />\n有啲人會覺得安全性成疑，<br />\n因 mcafee 嘅防毒本身就虧虧地，<br />\n我自己用過就覺得不過不失，<br />\n只係 iOS app 功能上略嫌太簡陋。<br />\n<br />\n2. NordVPN<br />\n有做年度安全審核，<br />\n亦有雙重 VPN，<br />\n但雙重 VPN 速度上慢過 Surfshark，<br />\n帳號唔支援 Surfshark 有嘅 2FA 雙重認證，<br />\n近年又經常有 AC 被流出，<br />\n而價錢上都無 Surfshark 咁平，<br />\n又無好似 Surfshark 咁可以同時連10幾20部機，<br />\n但勝在穩定性高過 Surfshark，<br />\n有 iKEv2、OpenVPN、連最新嘅 wireguard 都 support (亦即 NordLynx)，<br />\n伺服器數量更大幅拋離 Surfshark (5700+)，<br />\n多人用起上嚟相對上無咁易降速同唔穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">如果想用 NordVPN 但又怕自己 AC 被流出咁點算好？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n- 開新 email (推薦 protonmail or tutanota)<br />\n- 密碼要 15 位以上 (要有大細楷同數字連符號)<br />\n- 新 email 避免用作註冊其他網站或服務<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">簡單講下其他 VPN 嘅問題</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. ProtonVPN<br />\n- 貴，出海慢，雙重 VPN 更慢<br />\n<br />\n2. Mullvad<br />\n- 原生 APP 唔支援雙重 VPN<br />\n- 雙重 VPN 的 kill switch 功能僅支援 linux 上使用<br />\n- 月費同年費一樣價 (5 euro /m)，無優惠<br />\n<br />\n3. Surfshark<br />\n- 多咗人用穩定性變差<br />\n- CS 服務態度一般"},{"pid":"117fa4e929ceb8f5adaefa844ec738db369e7779","tid":2037914,"uid":73671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b9537547d2763258662ed4fc02f9a0dcd1f1d5","tid":2037914,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:47:56.000Z","msg":"咁protonmail / tutanota 有無必要做付費會員？<br />\n如果只單純申請vpn 用"},{"pid":"b0f15065bdb1c1b4210e8c3138c544849ad4ed04","tid":2037914,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117fa4e929ceb8f5adaefa844ec738db369e7779","tid":2037914,"uid":73671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b9537547d2763258662ed4fc02f9a0dcd1f1d5","tid":2037914,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:47:56.000Z","msg":"咁protonmail / tutanota 有無必要做付費會員？<br />\n如果只單純申請vpn 用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:09:32.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"c4fd2a23a18b461574161aa396785b02f3a54e9b","tid":2037914,"uid":73671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0f15065bdb1c1b4210e8c3138c544849ad4ed04","tid":2037914,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117fa4e929ceb8f5adaefa844ec738db369e7779","tid":2037914,"uid":73671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b9537547d2763258662ed4fc02f9a0dcd1f1d5","tid":2037914,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T23:47:56.000Z","msg":"咁protonmail / tutanota 有無必要做付費會員？<br />\n如果只單純申請vpn 用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T00:09:32.000Z","msg":"無"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T02:04:37.000Z","msg":"Thanks thanks <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e298f558f078841321b16a1a9f6a5f5d4d4b2e86","tid":2037914,"uid":303554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23cf7135113c21eca69f6e5